row.entry:
Where storage method is of the following: COMP for lossless compressed, RAW for lossless uncompressed, or LOSSY for lossy compressed followed by
 the quality level (0-100)
ex: image, "button.png" LOSSY 85;
ex: image, "backdrop.jpg" RAW;
